  <brief_title>Could Colour Dopper Improve the Diagnosis of Retained Placental Fragments After Second Trimester Miscarriage ?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Value of Pelvic Ultrasonography and Colour Doppler in Diagnosing Retained Placental Fragments After Mid Trimester Miscarriage</official_title>
